main event: A sighting of a large rocket-like object with a green tail was reported in Narrow Bridge, Washington, on 29 June 1956.
interesting points: The object resembled a sky rocket in flight,The object crossed a major portion of the sky in just 3 seconds,Multiple witnesses, including air defense personnel, observed the object,The object reportedly had a red front and a yellow back,The sighting occurred at night and involved various aircraft in the area.
sighted object: large sky rocket-like object with a green tail
witness description: members of air defense and other aircraft personnel
